  "relatedNotes": [
    "There is no dedicated parser-status polling endpoint. Re-fetch specification list/detail to observe ParseStatus changes.",
    "The planning docs for FE-03-03 describe a future async parser flow, but the current FE-facing API surface is still the 9 endpoints documented here."
  ]
}
